quran[11{c,v,t}:
18,35,"phir woh apni jannat mein daakhil howa aur apne nafs ke haq mein zalim ban kar kehnay laga"" mein nahi samjhta ke yeh doulat kabhi fanaa ho jaye gi"
18,36,"aur mujhe tawaqqa nahi ke qayamat ki gharri kabhi aeye gi taham agar kabhi mujhe apne rab ke huzoor پلٹایا bhi gaya to zaroor iss se bhi ziyada shandaar jagah paon ga """
18,37,"uss ke hamsaye ne guftagu karte hue is se kaha"" kya to kufar karta hai uss zaat se jis ne tujhe matti se aur phir nutfay se peda kya aur tujhe aik poora aadmi bana khara kya ?"
18,38,"raha mein, to mera rab to wohi Allah hai aur mein is ke sath kisi ko shareek nahi karta"
18,39,"aur jab to apni jannat mein daakhil ho raha tha to is waqt teri zabaan se yeh kyun nah nikla ke masha Allah , laa qoة ila ballh? agar to mujhe maal aur aulaad mein apne se kamtar pa raha hai"
18,40,to baeed nahi ke mera rab mujhe teri jannat se behtar ataa farma day aur teri jannat par aasman se koi aafat bhaij day jis se woh saaf maidan ban kar reh jaye
18,41,"ya is ka pani zameen mein utar jaye aur phir to usay kisi terhan nah nikaal sakay """
18,42,"aakhir kaar howa yeh ke is ka sara Samrah mara gaya aur woh apne angarro ke baagh ko tattyun( chappar) par ulta para dekh kar apni lagai hui laagat par haath milta reh gaya aur kehnay laga ke"" kash! mein ne apne rab ke sath kisi ko shareek nahTehraya hota """
18,43,"nah howa Allah ko chore kar is ke paas koi jatha ke is ki madad karta, aur nah kar saka woh aap hi is aafat ka muqaabla"
18,44,"uss waqt maloom howa ke karsazi ka ikhtiyar khuday-e brhq hi ke liye hai, inaam wohi behtar hai jo woh bakhshay aur injaam wohi bakhair hai jo woh dukhaay"
18,45,"aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! aِnhin hayaat duniya ki haqeeqat iss misaal se samjhao ke aaj hum ne aasman se pani barsa diya to zameen ki pod khob ghani ho gayi, aur kal wohi nabataat bhus ban kar reh gayi jisay hawae udaaye liye phurti hain Allah har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai"
